1
00:00:57,880 --> 00:00:59,340
What if this meteor shower

2
00:01:00,280 --> 00:01:01,920
fell right into my heart?

3
00:01:07,280 --> 00:01:08,480
I mean Wulan,

4
00:01:08,520 --> 00:01:09,840
Aunt Guli, and the others.

5
00:01:09,840 --> 00:01:11,120
They like you so much.

6
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,200
If you leave,

7
00:01:12,960 --> 00:01:14,480
they would be very sad.

8
00:01:16,760 --> 00:01:17,640
Don't worry.

9
00:01:17,960 --> 00:01:20,000
I'll make sure all the work is arranged

10
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,840
before I go.

11
00:01:37,120 --> 00:01:38,050
Okay. Thank you.

12
00:01:42,280 --> 00:01:43,080
Mr. Secretary.

13
00:01:43,080 --> 00:01:44,280
Why didn't you tell us

14
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,080
that Sister Ren Zhen is leaving?

15
00:01:50,960 --> 00:01:53,220
Don't let the villagers know about this.

16
00:01:53,280 --> 00:01:54,920
But why is she leaving?

17
00:01:56,360 --> 00:01:57,920
Why should she stay?

18
00:01:58,880 --> 00:02:00,600
Xiacun is our choice.

19
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,100
It doesn't mean it's hers.

20
00:02:02,600 --> 00:02:04,760
She has helped us enough these past few months.

21
00:02:04,760 --> 00:02:06,290
Since she chooses to leave,

22
00:02:06,520 --> 00:02:08,160
we should respect her.

23
00:02:08,360 --> 00:02:10,889
We shouldn't emotionally blackmail others.

24
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:14,600
Only three minutes left. Get ready.

25
00:02:14,600 --> 00:02:15,600
Wulan, come back.

26
00:02:26,880 --> 00:02:27,560
Start.

27
00:02:28,280 --> 00:02:29,040
Hello, everyone.

28
00:02:29,040 --> 00:02:31,320
I am Jiao Li, the First Secretary of Xia Village.

29
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,640
Today's live stream is

30
00:02:32,640 --> 00:02:34,240
from a yurt on the prairie.

31
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,460
We won't be introducing products

32
00:02:36,680 --> 00:02:38,210
or selling anything today.

33
00:02:38,320 --> 00:02:39,560
I'll tell you about

34
00:02:39,560 --> 00:02:41,120
the place where I grew up,

35
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:42,000
Bortala.

36
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,160
It has a temperate continental,

37
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,840
arid and semi-arid climate.

38
00:02:45,960 --> 00:02:48,280
There are plains, plateaus, and basins.

39
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:50,440
The most famous place here is

40
00:02:50,440 --> 00:02:51,400
Sayram Lake.

41
00:02:51,800 --> 00:02:53,880
It is the highest and largest

42
00:02:53,880 --> 00:02:55,880
alpine lake in Xinjiang.

43
00:03:08,440 --> 00:03:09,840
We have prairies,

44
00:03:10,000 --> 00:03:11,440
deserts, and the Gobi.

45
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:13,280
There's a saying that goes very well:

46
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,610
'To travel in Bozhou is to know Xinjiang.'

47
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,200
The clouds have no intent

48
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:29,260
to drift from the mountain peaks.

49
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,880
The birds are weary of flying

50
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,640
and know it's time to return.

51
00:03:34,840 --> 00:03:36,960
The shadows dim as twilight nears.

52
00:03:37,320 --> 00:03:40,079
I touch a lone pine and linger.

53
00:03:40,920 --> 00:03:41,760
Mr. Yin,

54
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:43,079
why are you here?

55
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,000
A whitefish.

56
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:49,170
I asked Lao Guo to save the biggest one.

57
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,180
Since you are leaving,

58
00:03:51,720 --> 00:03:53,000
I have to let you taste

59
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:55,240
the fresh fish of Sayram Lake before you go.

60
00:03:55,240 --> 00:03:56,600
Mr. Yin, I...

61
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,200
After Jiao Li finishes his broadcast,

62
00:03:58,200 --> 00:03:59,930
let's go home and eat together.

63
00:04:15,680 --> 00:04:16,810
Here comes the food.

64
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:18,560
Come on.

65
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,300
You all must be hungry.

66
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:23,840
It looks delicious.

67
00:04:24,440 --> 00:04:25,600
Eat it all up.

68
00:04:27,520 --> 00:04:28,440
This fish,

69
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,280
cost me a fortune.

70
00:04:36,040 --> 00:04:37,360
It's really delicious.

71
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,480
Then eat it all up.

72
00:04:40,080 --> 00:04:41,240
Thank you, Mr. Yin.

73
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,600
I remember the first time you two met

74
00:04:52,040 --> 00:04:53,040
was right here.

75
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,560
The three of us also had a meal together.

76
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:57,960
Time flies.

77
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,960
Now we're having a farewell meal.

78
00:05:03,560 --> 00:05:04,960
Your flight is tomorrow.

79
00:05:09,880 --> 00:05:10,720
Dad Yin,

80
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,800
I wish you all the best,

81
00:05:13,080 --> 00:05:15,080
and take care wherever you go.

82
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,020
Here, Ren Zhen,

83
00:05:24,520 --> 00:05:26,120
let me propose a toast to you.

84
00:05:27,200 --> 00:05:28,920
Thank you for coming to Xiacun.

85
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:29,840
Remember to

86
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:30,920
miss

87
00:05:30,920 --> 00:05:31,850
us in the future.

88
00:05:32,960 --> 00:05:33,760
Thank you.

89
00:05:38,280 --> 00:05:40,360
I won't forget every day I spent here

90
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,080
and every person

91
00:05:42,560 --> 00:05:44,200
I met.

92
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,320
After I go back,

93
00:05:45,320 --> 00:05:46,780
I might be busy for a while.

94
00:05:47,320 --> 00:05:48,240
When I have time,

95
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,770
I will come visit you again.

96
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:50,680
Okay.

97
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:53,360
It's a promise.

98
00:05:54,520 --> 00:05:55,360
It's a deal.

99
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:06,000
You don't need to see me off tomorrow.

100
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:08,600
I'm not good at handling goodbyes.

101
00:06:11,000 --> 00:06:12,160
You won't blame me

102
00:06:12,840 --> 00:06:15,440
for not telling Auntie Guli and the others, will you?

103
00:06:15,440 --> 00:06:16,640
Of course not.

104
00:06:17,400 --> 00:06:19,200
Thank you for not saying anything.

105
00:06:19,200 --> 00:06:20,200
I came quietly,

106
00:06:20,520 --> 00:06:21,850
and I'll leave quietly.

107
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:24,180
But you have to explain for me.

108
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:26,600
I'm not leaving because Xia Village is bad.

109
00:06:26,600 --> 00:06:27,800
Xia Village is great.

110
00:06:31,120 --> 00:06:31,920
Don't worry.

111
00:06:32,280 --> 00:06:33,560
I'll tell them.

112
00:06:35,760 --> 00:06:37,120
You don't blame me?

113
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:53,440
You go back first.

114
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:55,180
I'll stay a bit longer.

115
00:07:05,080 --> 00:07:05,840
Goodbye.

116
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,240
Ren Zhen.

117
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,400
You're not a hollow person.

118
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,920
You are a star person.

119
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,040
What?

120
00:07:53,200 --> 00:07:54,800
You are like a star,

121
00:07:55,480 --> 00:07:57,200
someone who shines brightly.

122
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:01,400
Thank you.

123
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:04,480
Go for it.

124
00:08:27,800 --> 00:08:29,200
Why are you guys here?

125
00:08:29,960 --> 00:08:32,419
Are you just going to let her leave like that?

126
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,159
She has her own choices,

127
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:40,960
and the right to make decisions.

128
00:08:41,799 --> 00:08:43,520
We can't force her to stay.

129
00:08:43,640 --> 00:08:44,900
Did you ask her to stay?

130
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,400
Yeah, did you?

131
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:48,800
Exactly. Did you ask Ren Zhen to stay?

132
00:08:48,800 --> 00:08:49,880
Did you?

133
00:09:05,960 --> 00:09:07,360
Why do you look like this?

134
00:09:08,080 --> 00:09:09,640
When you gave Ren Zhen

135
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,560
your blessing just now,

136
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:14,440
you weren't generous at all.

137
00:09:14,960 --> 00:09:17,020
If you really don't want her to leave,

138
00:09:17,280 --> 00:09:18,680
you should tell her.

139
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:20,440
Sir,

140
00:09:20,880 --> 00:09:23,410
I don't want to make things difficult for her.

141
00:09:23,440 --> 00:09:24,760
I belong here.

142
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:27,520
Coming back here is my mission and dream,

143
00:09:27,680 --> 00:09:29,340
but it doesn't mean it's hers.

144
00:09:31,680 --> 00:09:33,560
I don't want to be the one holding her back.

145
00:09:33,560 --> 00:09:35,440
I didn't ask you to hold her back.

146
00:09:35,680 --> 00:09:38,240
But you need to express your thoughts.

147
00:09:39,520 --> 00:09:41,400
Have you forgotten everything

148
00:09:41,720 --> 00:09:43,040
you learned in class?

149
00:09:44,240 --> 00:09:45,200
To speak insincerely,

150
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,800
or to speak from the heart,

151
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:49,480
which way of expression is better?

152
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,840
You should know.

153
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:05,700
We need to let her know.

154
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,690
At least we need to let her know.

155
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,600
Right?

156
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:09,720
Right, right.
